text: The City of Orange is a township in Essex County, New Jersey, United States. As of the 2020 United States Census, the township's population was 34,447. ==References== ==Other websites== * City of Orange Township website * Orange Board of Education * Data for the Orange Board of Education, National Center for Education Statistics * Citizens for Responsible Government website Category:Townships in New Jersey Category:Essex County, New Jersey
